    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Do I need a prescription?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes. A valid doctor prescription is required for all prescription
          medicines. For OTC and daily needs items, prescription is not needed.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h3>How do I place an order?</h3>
        <p>
          You can use the <a href="order.html">Order Now</a> form on our website
          or send us a message directly on WhatsApp with your details and prescription.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h3>How long will delivery take?</h3>
        <p>
          For most locations in Bhopal, we target delivery within around 2 hours
          of order confirmation, depending on stock, traffic and your exact area.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h3>Which areas do you serve?</h3>
        <p>
          Service is available all over Bhopal and nearby areas. You can share your
          location on WhatsApp to confirm coverage.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
        <p>
          We generally support Cash on Delivery and popular online payment options
          (like UPI). You can confirm the exact options with our team in chat.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h3>Are the medicines genuine?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes. All medicines are sourced from authorised, licensed pharmacies only
          and are billed properly with checked expiry dates.
        </p>
